{"tid":785261,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解一定要敬老？幾時開始尊重老野係必然？點解你做人耐過我就要老奉尊敬你？","createTime":"2018-08-19T05:17:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-19T17:17:03.000Z","uid":66260,"like":74,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"1e59f4d3ecdbf9af7a5e891efecc658e4ce7caef","tid":785261,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T05:17:16.000Z","msg":"「敬老」呢樣野根本就係劣質支那文化，你睇下幾多廢老抱住「敬老」呢種霸道思想恃老賣老？<br />\n尤其是關愛座呢樣嘢更加助長左唔少廢老既氣焰，令到唔少廢老拎住張長者卡就出街打橫咁制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢個世界人人平等，從來唔會有一個人無緣無故就比另一個人更值得人尊敬，你大我嗰幾廿歲更唔係我老奉要尊敬你嘅理由<br />\n由今日開始，我地要抵制「敬老」呢種唔平等嘅支那文化<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢一點外國人睇得透過你班支那人好多：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.quora.com/Why-should-we-respect-elders\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.quora.com%2FWhy-should-we-respect-elders&d=WD3TJfmzQAvkfIlhXWSmx7%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=c034aa4d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.quora.com/Why-should-we-respect-elders</a><br />\n<br />\nWe should not respect anybody who does not deserve respect, whether they are elders or not. And the only way to know <span style=\"color: red;\">who deserves respect is for people to demonstrate that they are worthy of respect</span>. This is another way of saying that people &quot;earn&quot; respect."},{"pid":"b2f98cae49a06267944bbaf2a2143c5c6b99a1d3","tid":785261,"uid":66260,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T05:29:52.000Z","msg":"頭先幫個妹妹出聲屌柒個廢老個位霸氣男，你真係好撚有型呀！！！<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/bvQsFS\" target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/bvQsFS</a><br />\n<br />\n睇見呢個post有感<br />\n其實都唔係第一單"},{"pid":"0c7452a940c7657ed87b927dd6f302dcf1f0b690","tid":785261,"uid":86841,"like":0,"dislike":30,"score":-30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T05:59:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"131d902b5773f658ee187fa875d3b5ce3c5af9a8","tid":785261,"uid":56308,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":